OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778043857
OL,3,CKate returns to international travel
OL,4,Cnext week with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FThe centre was founded by Kate in 2021
OL,7,Fto raise awareness of the importance
OL,8,Fof early years experiences in shaping
OL,9,Fsociety over the long term, and to
OL,10,Fcommission research.
OL,12,FThe announcement coincides with a
OL,13,Fvisit by Kate to the University of
OL,14,FEast London on Wednesday for the
OL,15,Flaunch of the centre's new resource
OL,16,Ffor people working with babies, young
OL,17,Fchildren and their families.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
