CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778043857
OL,3,CKate returns to international travel
OL,4,Cnext week with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FThe 109-page Foundations for Life
OL,7,Fsocial and emotional development guide
OL,8,Fis aimed at both practitioners and
OL,9,Fvolunteers.
OL,11,FPalace aides said both the publication
OL,12,Fand the trip signalled a milestone
OL,13,Fmoment for the princess and the
OL,14,Fcentre's work in early years both in
OL,15,Fthe UK and abroad.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
