CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778043857
OL,3,CKate returns to international travel
OL,4,Cnext week with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FIn its foreword, Kate writes: "While
OL,7,Four society often focuses on academic
OL,8,For physical milestones, research
OL,9,Fconsistently shows that it is our
OL,10,Fearliest relationships, experiences
OL,11,Fand environments which lay the
OL,12,Ffoundations for our future health and
OL,13,Fhappiness.
OL,15,F"The quality of our connections ` with
OL,16,Fourselves, with others and with the
OL,17,Fworld around us ` shapes how safe we
OL,18,Ffeel, how we relate, and how we
OL,19,Fprocess experiences throughout our
OL,20,Flives."
OL,26,@nD@_OUwD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
