PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778043857
OL,3,CKate returns to international travel
OL,4,Cnext week with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FShe adds: "By age five, our brains
OL,7,Fhave already grown to 90% of their
OL,8,Fadult size... making early childhood a
OL,9,Fcritical window for developing the
OL,10,Fsocial and emotional skills that
OL,11,Fbecome the bedrock of lifelong
OL,12,Fwellbeing."
OL,14,FIn the coming months, the centre will
OL,15,Fwork with early years leaders to embed
OL,16,Fthe understanding into entry-level
OL,17,Ftraining and ongoing professional
OL,18,Fdevelopment.
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
