OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778043857
OL,3,CKate returns to international travel
OL,4,Cnext week with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FIt is not yet known whether the
OL,7,Fprincess will join him but her return
OL,8,Fto foreign tours will raise hopes a
OL,9,Ftrip across the Atlantic could happen
OL,10,Ffor the Waleses, following in the
OL,11,Ffootsteps of the King's high-profile
OL,12,FUS state visit to see Donald Trump
OL,13,Flast week.
OL,15,FKate was diagnosed with an undisclosed
OL,16,Fform of cancer early in 2024, for
OL,17,Fwhich she underwent chemotherapy, and
OL,18,Fshe announced she was in remission 16
OL,19,Fmonths ago in January 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
