FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778043857
OL,3,CKate returns to international travel
OL,4,Cnext week with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FShe has gradually returned to royal
OL,7,Fduties, including supporting the King
OL,8,Fat state visits to the UK, and last
OL,9,Fmonth joined the royal family to mark
OL,10,Fthe 100th anniversary of the late
OL,11,FQueen Elizabeth II's birth, and made a
OL,12,Fsolo appearance at the Cenotaph on
OL,13,FAnzac Day.
OL,15,FThe Waleses' last major lengthy tour
OL,16,Ftogether was their controversial trip
OL,17,Fto the Caribbean in March 2022 to
OL,18,Fcelebrate the Platinum Jubilee, before
OL,19,Fthey spent three days in Boston in
OL,20,FDecember 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
